signatureAbility.signatureDescription: The game's top defenders excel in all situations. When they enter the zone, this ability increases their chance of defeating run blocks, and disrupting catches via tackles.
Defenders with this ability use faster run shed moves for a better chance at shedding blocks against inside run plays.
Defenders with this ability can apply pressure to the quarterback from a greater distance.
Defenders with this ability will frequently prevent additional yardage gains while tackling
Blockers with this ability will frequently attempt and win pull blocks
Blockers with this ability will frequently attempt and win impact blocks against linebackers and defensive backs when playing as a lineman or fullback.
Blockers with this ability reduce a rusher's chances of using a quick block shed move while run blocking.
Ballcarriers with this ability have more powerful stiff arm animations and have a larger timing window for landing perfect stiff arms.
Ballcarriers with this ability have steerable juke animations.
Running Backs with this ability receive improved blocking from their O-Line within 5 yards of the end zone
Players with this ability are much less likely to be fooled by WR runoffs
Players with this ability are more likely to succeed at and attempt diving catches and swats.
Defenders with this ability force more catch tackle knockouts in man-to-man versus short routes less than 10 yards from LoS
